            <description><![CDATA[Version 0.0.7 of the ITB API introduces enhanced traceability and version tracking capabilities for model exports.]]></description>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Version 0.0.7 of the ITB API introduces enhanced traceability and version tracking capabilities for model exports.</p>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>Part of ITB 0.0.7 release</strong> - See <a class="" href="https://itb.banian.ch/docs/changelog/itb-0.0.7">master release</a> and <a class="" href="https://itb.banian.ch/docs/changelog-webapp/webapp-0.0.7">WebApp Details</a></p>
</blockquote>
<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="-new-features">✨ New Features<a href="https://itb.banian.ch/docs/changelog-api/api-0.0.7#-new-features" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to ✨ New Features" title="Direct link to ✨ New Features" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<h3 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="metadata-export-file">Metadata Export File<a href="https://itb.banian.ch/docs/changelog-api/api-0.0.7#metadata-export-file" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to Metadata Export File" title="Direct link to Metadata Export File" translate="no">​</a></h3>
<p>Model exports now automatically include a <code>_metadata.json</code> file that captures comprehensive version information and statistics about the exported model.</p>
<p><strong>What's included:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li class=""><strong>Version information:</strong> ITB frontend, API, and library versions</li>
<li class=""><strong>Export timestamp:</strong> When the model was exported</li>
<li class=""><strong>Statistics:</strong> Entity, relation, viewpoint, and node counts</li>
</ul>
<h3 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="new-api-endpoint-pb_info">New API Endpoint: <code>/pb_info</code><a href="https://itb.banian.ch/docs/changelog-api/api-0.0.7#new-api-endpoint-pb_info" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to new-api-endpoint-pb_info" title="Direct link to new-api-endpoint-pb_info" translate="no">​</a></h3>
<p>A new endpoint has been added to retrieve version information from PocketBase (ITB Frontend):</p>
<ul>
<li class=""><strong>Method:</strong> GET</li>
<li class=""><strong>Path:</strong> <code>/pb_info</code></li>
<li class=""><strong>Returns:</strong> JSON with current version information</li>
</ul>
<p>This endpoint calls the PocketBase <code>/getVersion</code> hook to retrieve the current version of the ITB frontend.</p>
<h3 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="example-metadata-file">Example Metadata File<a href="https://itb.banian.ch/docs/changelog-api/api-0.0.7#example-metadata-file" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to Example Metadata File" title="Direct link to Example Metadata File" translate="no">​</a></h3>
